    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >梦眼</h2>探索一系列多样化的机制驱动梦境。《<strong>梦眼<i>（以及其他）</i></strong>》是一款单人游戏<i>（始终如此）</i>，第一人称<i>（通常）</i>，游戏<i>（大概）</i>。《<strong>梦眼</strong>》采用<i><u>可选的</u></i>眼部追踪技术，使用你的日常摄像头。通过现实中眨眼这一物理动作，你周围的世界随之改变，灵感源自我们每日脑海中播放的电影那不可预测的本质。<br><br><br>                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201420/extras/269e6fc8deca4a60cd1b6128997a270e.poster.avif?t=1755554187\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201420/extras/269e6fc8deca4a60cd1b6128997a270e.webm?t=1755554187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201420/extras/269e6fc8deca4a60cd1b6128997a270e.mp4?t=1755554187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >熟悉的焦虑</h2>梦境彼此相连，你的路径将根据每个世界的结果而分岔。其中的谜题采用全新方式，通常隐藏操作方式，迫使玩家跳出既定思维，直面自己与游戏的关系以及对&quot;控制权&quot;的期待。 <br><br><br>                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201420/extras/2bbe7794f520acb832c99a4bb1dbc1d8.poster.avif?t=1755554187\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201420/extras/2bbe7794f520acb832c99a4bb1dbc1d8.webm?t=1755554187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201420/extras/2bbe7794f520acb832c99a4bb1dbc1d8.mp4?t=1755554187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不可预知</h2>遇见并帮助栖息在这些世界中的独特角色，发现隐藏其下的深层联系。帮助他们，或许他们也会帮助你……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感谢阅读，期待与你相遇！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201420/extras/fb75b72c3476e50f0c2abd2ea3d12144